### Apex RAG Lab — Query samples (REST format)
### Use com VS Code extensao "REST Client" ou Postman/Insomnia.
### Substitua {SEARCH_ENDPOINT} e {QUERY_KEY} pelos seus valores capturados no cap 06.

@searchEndpoint = https://srch-apex-rag-lab-{aluno}.search.windows.net
@queryKey = SEU_QUERY_KEY_AQUI
@indexName = kb-apex-index
@apiVersion = 2024-07-01

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Cenario 1 — Keyword search puro (BM25)
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/docs/search?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
api-key: {{queryKey}}

{
  "search": "devolução",
  "top": 5,
  "select": "chunk,source_file,title"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Cenario 2 — Stemming portugues (analyzer pt-Lucene)
### "horarios" matches "horario" via stemming
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/docs/search?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
api-key: {{queryKey}}

{
  "search": "horários",
  "top": 5,
  "select": "chunk,source_file"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Cenario 3 — Filter por source_file
### Buscar so dentro de um PDF especifico
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/docs/search?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
api-key: {{queryKey}}

{
  "search": "prazo",
  "filter": "source_file eq 'politica_reembolso_lojista.pdf'",
  "top": 5,
  "select": "chunk,source_file,title"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Cenario 4 — Semantic ranker (re-ranking neural)
### Query natural em portugues
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/docs/search?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
api-key: {{queryKey}}

{
  "search": "quanto tempo eu tenho pra devolver um produto?",
  "queryType": "semantic",
  "semanticConfiguration": "kb-apex-semantic",
  "top": 5,
  "select": "chunk,source_file,title"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Cenario 5 — Semantic ranker + answers + captions + highlight
### Modo RAG canonico — pronto para integrar em frontend
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/docs/search?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json
api-key: {{queryKey}}

{
  "search": "posso devolver produto perecível?",
  "queryType": "semantic",
  "semanticConfiguration": "kb-apex-semantic",
  "captions": "extractive|highlight-true",
  "answers": "extractive|count-3",
  "highlight": "chunk",
  "top": 5,
  "select": "chunk,source_file,title"
}

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Bonus — Service stats (verificar saude do servico)
### Use admin key para esta chamada (nao query key)
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{searchEndpoint}}/servicestats?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: SEU_ADMIN_KEY_AQUI

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Bonus — Index stats (document count, storage size)
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{searchEndpoint}}/indexes/{{indexName}}/stats?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: SEU_ADMIN_KEY_AQUI

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Bonus — Indexer status (apos run)
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{searchEndpoint}}/indexers/kb-apex-indexer/status?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: SEU_ADMIN_KEY_AQUI

### --------------------------------------------------------------------
### Bonus — Trigger indexer run manual
### --------------------------------------------------------------------
POST {{searchEndpoint}}/indexers/kb-apex-indexer/run?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: SEU_ADMIN_KEY_AQUI
